Instruction:

Below are the commands (lower cases) to interact with the application

- To add an order to shopping cart:
==> [number] [goods name] at [price]
For example: 8 bottle of perfume at 18.99

- To print the invoice:
==> print

- To empty the shopping cart:
==> empty

- To list the tax free goods
==> taxfree

- To register a goods as taxfree
==> taxfree [goods name]
For example: taxfree chocolates

- To empty the taxfree goods list:
==> empty taxfree

- To exit the application:
==> exit